{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"overview","title":"Overview","subLink":null},{"id":"overview","title":"Overview","subLink":[]},{"id":"contosouniversityrestapi","title":"Contoso University REST API","subLink":[]}],"title":"Overview","description":"","validatorType":"decorators","validationTypeTitle":"Decorators","type":"simple","gitDocPath":"https://github.com/rxweb/rxweb.io/edit/master/docs/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/overview.md","category":"tours-of-contoso-app","subCategory":null,"linkTitle":"overview","tabArray":{},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<div class='row page-section' id= 'overview'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Overview<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/tours-of-contoso-app/overview#overview'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >As we all are very familiar with the <span class='highlighted'>\"Contoso University\"</span>, we are going to demonstrate the same application through RxWebCore so that we'll be able to relate the same more efficiently.</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'contosouniversityrestapi'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Contoso University REST API<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/tours-of-contoso-app/overview#contosouniversityrestapi'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >In this complete <span class='highlighted'>Beginner</span> section of <span class='highlighted'>Tours of Contoso App</span>, we'll walkthrough the guide to develop a sample web application on Contoso University which included the functionality of managing courses and their enrolled students in which you can perform the complete Web API operation including GET, PUT, POST, DELETE and PATCH with proper authentication and autherization of every user.</p>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Here is the created REST API shown below: </p>\r\n<img src='/assets/rxwebcore/Images/overview-tours-of-contoso.PNG' alt='Swagger Api'>\r\n<p class=\"image-description\">REST Api</p>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >In this contoso application tour, you will learn:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/creating-tables\">Creating Tables</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/creating-views\">Creating Views</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/create-the-project\">Project Creation</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/authentication\">User Authentication</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/scaffolding/models\">Model Scaffolding</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/scaffolding/context-and-uow\">Creating DbContext and UOW</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/scaffolding/creating-api\">Creating API</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/authorization\">Authorization</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/data-validation\">Data Validation</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a href=\"/rx-web-core/tours-of-contoso-app/Beginner/test-the-api\">Testing the API</a></li>\r\n  <li class=\"overview-nav-item\"><a>Deploying the API</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}